text: Jan Kawulok (born 27 January 1946) is a Polish skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1968 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1946 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Poland Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:People from Wisła
